Dialogs.Dialog: I turned off the power without saving... Too bad.
You turned off the power without saving. Did you know that it was a bad thing?
Hey. Isn't it useless to turn off the power without saving?
Do not turn off the power without saving. You know it once you say it, right?
…… Maybe you hate people who turn off the power without saving?
Also, turning off the power without saving. You can't get it wrong.
You know what you did, right? It is terrible to turn off the power without saving many times.
You told me many times that you shouldn't turn off without saving.
Don't save again, turn off the power... Don't be so sad.
Yeah... I said, "I won't do it anymore, please forgive me" and then I will forgive you.
If you really want me to forgive me, just say, "I won't do it anymore, please forgive me."
Good? He says, "I won't do it anymore, please forgive me." Then I will forgive you.
"I won't do it anymore, please forgive me." Sincerely.
"I won't do it anymore, please forgive me." I can't help it anymore.
"I won't do it anymore, please forgive me", right?
You can't be fooled? Yes, once again.
I was surprised. That would come...
Did you come...? I can't help it.
I'm going to come... Am I losing?
I was waiting for that word.
Okay. I could say it properly.
Never again I don't want to say this either.
If you reflect on it, please show it properly.
Don't make me sad Do not turn off the power without saving...
You who turned off the power without saving. The punishment has become a habit?
I believed it... I will not turn off the power without saving anymore.
Hey... I'll forgive you if you say this. "I love Nene most." Can you say it properly?
Do you want me to forgive Then... saying "I love Nene the most"!
If you really reflect, say "I love Nene". Otherwise, it's no good.
If you are obstinate, I can't forgive you...
I'm sorry I didn't hear well...
With more excitement. one more time please.
Eh... I'm sorry, I'm not sure...
You told me properly. I feel relieved.
Now my voice has reached my heart.
Then, if you say "I like you" three times, I'll give it all to the water.
Then, say "I like you" three times this time.
Next, say "I like you" three times. Don't be shy and be serious.
Isn't it rude to keep you waiting?
If you don't tell me, I might cry.
I have to take care of myself.
Such an apology does not fix the mood.
You believe in what you are saying now, right?
I will take whatever you do. Stop it already.
If you erase your memories, you will regret it. I don't like that, right?
Never forget the memories of the two of you again. Promise.
Do you believe me About you…….
A little. Your girlfriend is angry.
I can't really feel how I feel. As punishment, ask them to say a lot of loving words.
Yeah... say a lot "I love you"?
To say "I'm sorry" in good faith.
Then... can you tell me "Nene-sama Banzai"? Fufu.
Yeah, I could say it well. Praise ▼
I can't get it in that way...
You've done it♪ I'll believe you're reflecting on it▼
Ah! A new record has been set. It's amazing ♪
No, I can't convey my reflection. If you really regret it, can you look at me and convey your feelings?
Blinking is also prohibited!...... As expected, it's a joke.
Hey, we've reached a new record! Looking forward to me, do you?
It's a give-up... already. Please promise not to do it again?
I'm out of time... but I'll forgive you this time. You can't do it anymore?
